\subsection{Costs}

\subsubsection{A troubadour must spend (50 + 100 \x Rank)
Silver Pennies per year to supply himself with the props necessary for
his trade.}

A troubadour who does not spend the above amount operates as if he
were two Ranks less proficient. If the rank of a troubadour is
reduced to a negative number, the use of the skill is temporarily
lost.
